Welcome to the To-Do List App!

This guide will help you get started with using the app to manage your tasks effectively.

1. Adding a Task:

Step 1: Click on the input field where it says "Add a new task...".
Step 2: Type the task you want to add.
Step 3: Click the "+" button or press Enter on your keyboard. The task will be added to the list.
2. Marking a Task as Complete:

Step 1: Locate the task you have completed in the list.
Step 2: Click on the checkbox next to the task. The task will be marked as complete and visually crossed out.
3. Deleting a Task:

